PersonalMission.Name: MT-9: A Worthy Opponent
PersonalMission.Description: Seeking and destroying enemy heavy tanks is a hard task to accomplish but very beneficial to the team's cause.
PersonalMission.Hint: Outflank enemy vehicles, shoot them while concealed, target their weak spots to pick them apart—whatever it takes. Remember that heavy tanks are slower than you, and their turrets have low traverse speeds.

Primary.Conditions:
• Cause at least 1,500 HP of damage to enemy heavy tanks.
• Destroy at least 2 enemy heavy tanks.

Secondary.Conditions:
• Survive the battle.
• Win the battle.
